summary:
It's a gift from the Gods themselves.

Praying does pay off. You can thank the Gods for this gift from the heavens. Its sweetness is beyond any human-baked sweetroll.

It's an edible sweetroll that gives you usefull bonuses. And its BIG.
descriptionHtml:
Praying does pay off. You can thank the Gods for this gift from the heavens. Its sweetness is beyond any human-baked sweetroll.

It's an edible sweetroll that gives you usefull bonuses. And its BIG.

Location: Throat of the World - Next to the dragon wall
If you want more type this in the console : player.additem 5E000D63 x
x = how much you want of them


P.S - No, its not a porn mod !
